  <span id="freeText7135231316605246796" style="display:none">I consider this to be essential reading. For everyone. The concepts can be a bit dense, but it's well worth the effort. Combined with <i>A Book of Five Rings</i> by Miyamoto Musashi and <i>The Art of War</i> by Sun Tzu, this is part of a set that I frequently give to people.</span>
