<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15798827-the-essential-dogen"><img alt="The Essential Dogen: Writings of the Great Zen Master" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344619027l/15798827._SX98_.jpg" />
